Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這個表情 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.60,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻譯：梅子 NG 熊貓 校對：小白 影子 後期：風大 時間：果凍 壓制 風 A4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是我們事務所的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有男孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和惠惠拍雙人照的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要求有點難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會找找看的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:36.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday　言葉がたりなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:36.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 言語不足以表達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:46.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すれ違ったとしても やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:46.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使詞不達意 也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:53.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとわかりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:53.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:06.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時にひとりになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:06.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時 想一人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:18.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅をしても心は埋まらない そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:18.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使旅行 內心的空虛也無法填補
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:23.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切な人に気づくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:23.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我意識到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:27.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:27.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每時每刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:34.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　うまくいくとは限らない毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:34.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有點小挫折的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你微笑面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:48.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たったひとことがどれほど嬉しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:48.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多麼令我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:53.72,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:53.72,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日我也無法忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小傢伙防備心明明很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它其實很粘人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為害羞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 突然咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服了它就會咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它 沒討厭我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 它很纏你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果討厭你根本就不會讓你摸它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也會很纏我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突…突然間說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}短信 黑澤凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…那個…我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回條短信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒會回的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回去的時候有什麼打算麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要順便去哪裡逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有點事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接連兩天都被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拒絕…可是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們遇到什麼好事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和真討厭 好色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和你們倆很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和橘很順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把幸福展現出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我和麻美這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 健志好討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭就討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能和麻美在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(836,108)}黑澤凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(746,156)}梅也做得出來的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(698,172)}材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(874,250)}麵粉     120g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(856,280)}雞蛋     1個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(860,316)}無鹽黃油 30g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(842,344)}砂糖     30g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(672,362)}做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(900,448)}1.把麵粉篩好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(960,524)}2.用微波爐把黃油加熱至柔軟\N(不要讓它完全化掉哦)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 怎麼做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在每個步驟中都投入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕麻煩 只要認認真真來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然就會很好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我果然還是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把梅也做得來的食譜發給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 算了吧 我是做不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們交換郵箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(546,560)\frz344.993}我可不許你做奇怪的東西\N給哥哥吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中西他們真是超甜蜜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜蜜的氣氛都滿滿地溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們幸福 我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑澤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫不出大和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 還不習慣只叫名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會讓你叫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做好準備哦 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…把麵粉篩好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再和面 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用篩子篩麵粉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太難得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽你回來得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我有跟你說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是餅乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給男朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 麵粉放多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 聽說已經去辦公室打過招呼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈嘍 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事務所離得也近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼惠惠會在我們學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好找到不錯的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搬過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜拜嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 大和 你聽說了沒 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠 是惠惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 什麼惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠就是惠惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你過來看看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dessert雜誌的王牌讀者模特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川惠轉到咱們學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠…惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠臉好小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苗條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的轉學過來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定好去哪班了沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 這是我的手機號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不許搶先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 雖然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家通訊錄已經存滿了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(626,274)\c&HA39CE1&\3c&HEDEDED&}通訊錄已滿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(632,592)\4c&HE4E5EC&}記錄 500/500
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 下次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後給惠惠發短信 惠惠會很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很突然…大和君有女朋友麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直說了 我也想做大和君的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對大和君一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像找到了自己的白馬王子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們倆會交往得很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是俊男美女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 對這種只看外表的女人一點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我說了很沒禮貌的話 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不知道你有這麼相愛的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…請你把我當成普通的同班同學看待…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們願意的話…我想和你們倆成為好朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我並不介意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也說得太過分了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦 心裡的結終於解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 你們之間發生了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒發生過~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道就去問大和君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊大和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不在意昨天發生了什麼麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那個…發生什麼事了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別這麼簡單就相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真的是什麼事都沒發生 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠的校服到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 終於有校服穿了 超開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠穿得真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 D班下節課是生物吧？要換教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼？生物教室在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠還不清楚教室在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能陪她一起去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼 謝謝你大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惠惠！ 真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤君和惠惠好配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都好有型嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惠惠走在一起的大和 想想是不是覺得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我才剛來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校園裡還暈頭轉向的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家又不太會來跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 和雜誌模特在同一個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肯定都不敢和你搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想 大和君也能當模特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們事務所好像正在找男模呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君要不要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事 大和君肯定馬上就會火的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算不是殺人凶器了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是味道這關了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在每個步驟中都投入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己投入感情了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連貓都不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓都不吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別洩氣別洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和要當模特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要當模特啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去打一天的工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川的事務所的男模不夠 正發愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法拒絕啊…況且只去一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君肯定適合當模特~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 那是不是會給他化妝拍照啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦 要不要來攝影棚參觀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 北川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般沒什麼機會看的的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠的攝影現場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 這會給攝影棚的人添麻煩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常有人來參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡的話那我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不喜歡 感覺很難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們事務所的人說拍攝前想開個小會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學之後有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟梅一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意我 說不定是很要緊的事 你還是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有每天必須一起回家的規定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們社長看到照片之後就很中意大和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非吵著要見一面 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有一個人回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是和黑澤在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一步都感覺好漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎麼盡想這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主題是 戀人約會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加進去點動作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亮了麼？怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不換照明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就讓他們拿包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 很專業的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠他們還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 惠惠好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厲害啊 這就是所謂的特別氣場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 有氣場麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和也準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超難為情的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮造型亂亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像和喜歡的人在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 再高興點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和很有潛質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦 我說有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和真像個專業模特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惠惠看起來像真的情侶似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額…這是設定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人再靠近點 牽個手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對 緊緊握住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人簡直絕配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是超出預料了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠今天看起來也很在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們邊上看著的人都感覺心跳加速了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和這麼奪目 這裡的氣氛又這麼歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼盡想這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大和會越走越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:49.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(736,478)}「為什麼…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:11.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\be3}慣れきた表情の　冷たい朝が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:11.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}喜歡能看到你熟悉表情的清冷早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:17.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}あからさまなった意図みせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:17.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}如此直率地向我表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:24.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}予言のような空の色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:24.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}天空的顏色如預言般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:29.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}そんなに意地悪しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:29.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}不要這樣的捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:35.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}笑った薄い唇に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:35.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}你的薄唇邊掛著微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}傾く影を追いかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}我追尋著你傾斜的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:47.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}君さえもわからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:47.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}即使我還對你一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:55.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}頼りない　もっと抱きしめて放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:55.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}雖然不可靠 但請自由地擁抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:59.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}重ねていくいつもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:59.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}總會有許多的交匯處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}頼りないぐらい　不器用なslow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}雖然不可靠 笨拙的slow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:12.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}揺れる気持ちを乗るの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:12.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}但還是希望你能跟著搖曳的心一起走下去

Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和去做模特 我為什麼會莫名地不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心點開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀吼~好興奮啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 難過的時候可以抱抱我喵~
